snippet.title: AIPD - GDC 2015 Trailer
snippet.description: Thanks to Epic Games, we've been given the phenomenal chance to show off our debut title AIPD - Artificial Intelligence Police Department at the Unreal Engine Booth at this year's GDC in San Francisco. Hurray. If you are there, be sure to stop by and say hello. Consider following us on twitter @blabadger and facebook: www.fb.com/blazingbadger
